{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend visas for 3 more years for business applications under the Turkish ECAA.",
        "additional_details": "In the coming weeks due to the Coronavirus pandemic, huge numbers of people may be laid off, get their hours cut and may not have a way to pay their rent, mortgage or bills.\r\nWe would like the Home Office to allow automatic 3 years visa renewal to all ECAA applicants and allow them to be employed should they find it difficult to continue their businesses under the circumstances.",
        "background": "After completing one year of self-employment\r\nTurkish applicants must normally be granted 3 years\u2019\r\nvisa if the provisions are met -\r\nwhere the ongoing success of the business is\r\nstill to be proven. With Coronavirus pandemic, it would be difficult to continue a successful businesses.",
